    See all 74 reviews5.0 out of 5 starsFast-paced thriller with great characters and important plotBySara Watsonon August 24, 2016Format: Paperback|Verified PurchasePepper clearly fulfills the adage "write what you know."  This thriller is rich with details and has a plot that is all too plausible in today's world.  The dialogue is engaging and real.  The book reveals our system for those who aren't familiar with it, and it's a rollicking read for those who are.  I especially like having a lead character worth rooting for.  Strongly recommended.0Comment|
