"I purchased your product Napa Valley Homemade Marinara.  I’ve never used a bottled sauce in the 50 years I’ve been married!  (I am of Italian extractio and always made my own home sauce)  Your sauce is excellent! I just made a cacciatore dinner and used your sauce and it came out scrumptious!" 
										Elena, Pueblo, CO





